      "role": "user",
      "content": "The train/bus thing sounds like it'll take way too long though. I really just need to find the most direct flight alternatives. Like, should I be looking for connecting flights through hubs like Dubai or Doha, or is it better to just try and find another direct from Heathrow? I'm just trying to figure out how to minimize the delays.",
